{"tid":926686,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[單身入]其他人同你講將來，你會唔會覺得好無冇意思？","createTime":"2018-12-03T15:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T08:23:34.000Z","uid":89394,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27f2d7c75a36e6bffc27a341b2f57061e1576762","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"早幾日有隻保險狗sell我叫我買儲錢單<br />\n話而家後生草錢，將來有啲咩事都可以用<br />\n<br />\n但講真<br />\n當我唔覺得自己會有自己家庭時<br />\n我五六十歲拎住果舊咁嘅錢<br />\n都唔知有乜用<br />\n<br />\n一來，我無家庭都無乜必要出去買層樓（果舊錢買唔買到另計），加上而家老豆老母都有層樓可以夠住<br />\n二來，話有咩大病可以有錢醫病，我一條友醫黎做乜鳩，老豆老母又唔等住我養（而且我仲有個妹本身好痴屋企，老豆份工有份退休金又夠兩老慢慢摵到百年歸老）<br />\n三來，又話咩可以用黎退休用。屌，而家愈來愈大就覺得自己愈來愈無要求，我到時真係要咁多錢jm9，都冇力去享受世界<br />\n四來，又話咩用黎完成夢想。收皮啦，十幾廿年後個夢想都落後咗啦屌<br />\n<br />\n根本當一個人咩為將來打算乜乜柒係bull shit<br />\n啲錢草撚完都貶值<br />\n自己又冇晒青春享受<br />\n<br />\n果日同條保險狗傾到喊咗出嚟<br />\n根本將來出咩事，我唔係要錢<br />\n而係想自殺了結一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0bbfebe6273428fc6b4dba66b18f1da2e789a8","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:34:57.000Z","msg":"而家有錢只係想用晒黎做晒自己想做嘅嘢 想試嘅嘢<br />\n做完就無憾咁死<br />\n（雖然可能無組織家庭都係種遺憾，但都冇法強求，所以自己能做嘅襯仲有青春就做晒佢算）"},{"pid":"20668ecd425db11e04905fbcf9593f6bbcb3abf7","tid":926686,"uid":48769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"錢如果買得到快樂，這是值得的。<br />\n如果不用錢也得到快樂，這會更好嗎？"},{"pid":"d743540e3ef213059a9bdc9438c9ae799f685236","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20668ecd425db11e04905fbcf9593f6bbcb3abf7","tid":926686,"uid":48769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"錢如果買得到快樂，這是值得的。<br />\n如果不用錢也得到快樂，這會更好嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"錢只係令我覺得無咁抑鬱<br />\n但如果唔係即時<br />\n即係話有病唔係即刻食藥，而係草起啲藥<br />\n咁都係死"},{"pid":"6f8b644dd5b576fa421860381e660c49838a8e94","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"而家淨係想拎晒啲錢買衫、扮靚<br />\n見到鐘意嘅野買得起都唔理價錢買咗先<br />\n<br />\n實行同香港一樣玩焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e02c691283ca6136170bce46502482e268a0b9","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8bcda53dd0d22b52c2173043db6c3fbad95cffc","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30cd9d842e453bffae13362f78ee7b18700b003f","tid":926686,"uid":63845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"姑婆屋"},{"pid":"d3af4e8e9da0af054424bb5b714c456fd707bc1f","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30cd9d842e453bffae13362f78ee7b18700b003f","tid":926686,"uid":63845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"姑婆屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"係你害我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa38f486553a17fe1d6aed7590194cc2292e7c8","tid":926686,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30cd9d842e453bffae13362f78ee7b18700b003f","tid":926686,"uid":63845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"姑婆屋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T18:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e9e1b8310f77b11246dfed5aa20179f9860660","tid":926686,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aa38f486553a17fe1d6aed759